{"tid":1469444,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家做乜都好都唔會影響到機場世界級嘅地位","createTime":"2019-08-14T01:52:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T02:02:31.000Z","uid":133324,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"70510c9c09216386b4d5d0d4c458fbf8d7fc7dfa","tid":1469444,"uid":133324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:52:21.000Z","msg":"對唔住我係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">標題黨</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">核爆也不割</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無論如何，經過尋晚大家都會覺得影響機場客運有利有弊。利係高曝光有noise，呢個同時都係弊。唔知大家記唔記得張建宗同波叔個記者會，香港GDP<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">21%係出入口</span></span>，得<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">4%係旅遊</span></span>！香港機場係國際級，係因為我地<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">貨運量係全球第一</span></span>！！！超級一號貨運站更加係世界級中嘅世界級。<br />\n<br />\n發夢去咗超級一號貨運站參觀，真係好感動！客運主力做文宣同形象工程！發夢去第二度！"},{"pid":"23762fd1b764438607f227776ef1386753e2a86d","tid":1469444,"uid":133324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:52:47.000Z","msg":"自推十次"},{"pid":"2cc9108e4a0e72b5f7fd6304f75e1bae590d529b","tid":1469444,"uid":133324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:53:07.000Z","msg":"自推十次"},{"pid":"44a1cfe2ce7e08584bc797e81c8525a3d52f9ef9","tid":1469444,"uid":133324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:53:32.000Z","msg":"自推十次"},{"pid":"ec7aa4ec9861d7cec89a07525a099405d713bcb2","tid":1469444,"uid":133324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:54:02.000Z","msg":"自推十次"},{"pid":"bfe752d376856d561bfac304cb97e9de40ae0826","tid":1469444,"uid":133324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:54:31.000Z","msg":"自推十次"},{"pid":"f003dcf17aa43b7a25c881958168d12d376e79d4","tid":1469444,"uid":1333